articles.title: Vietnam detects a 'very dangerous' hybrid coronavirus variant that spreads quickly - ABC News
articles.description: Vietnam says the strain is a combination of the UK and Indian variants and spreads more quickly by air, as the South-East Asian country grapples with a rise in coronavirus cases.
articles.content:
Authorities in Vietnam have detected a new coronavirus variant that is a combination of the Indian and UK COVID-19 variants and spreads quickly by air, the country's health minister says.
